result.name: Alto

reviews.text:
A decent and fairly-priced brunch spot. It’s especially good for vegetarians with the choice of Impossible burgers and other non-meat options.

Salad bar/buffet had a solid selection but nothing mindblowing. The seafood wasn’t that tasty and the dessert options definitely need to improve (although you do get to choose a dessert from the brunch menu). Avoid the French Toast here though; it tasted awful compared to everything else we had.

Drinks selection is good but I don’t recall them having a beer. However, the cocktails were tasty, so I didn’t mind so much. 

The view is amazing. Make sure to ask for a window table when booking.
Great views over Hong Kong.  Happy Hour is good value.  Snacks are quite good.
My second time having lunch here, just love the salad bar and the good quality steak with the stunning view, don’t forget to make reservation.

A restaurant where you can enjoy nice view of hk but meanwhile the food is around average. The sirloin I ordered was quite average but the tuna tartare was good. Rather big food portion size. Staff are helpful too. 

However, the rooftop bar is a highlight. I have been there a few times and every time I went there I had a good time. Highly recommended.
Great view with good food which can include a buffet.  Service is good and the vibe is trendy.  Relaxing place to eat to get away from the busy streets.

result.adr_address: 31/F, V Point, 18 Tang Lung St, Causeway Bay, 香港
result.formatted_address: 31/F, V Point, 18 Tang Lung St, Causeway Bay, 香港
result.name: Alto

reviews.text:
忍住團火食呢餐生日飯！冇諗過坐位係咁逼，同隔檯咁近，上菜又冇位擺。菜又唔得，服務態度又差，都唔知想點？！

坐低已經有麵包，點完菜就食住等，麵包油到拎上手咬左一啖已經冇再食。

點左杯好似糖水嘅果汁？！味道又怪🥴

隔左陣就嚟左個頭盆crab cake (蟹肉餅) 呢個正常冇事。

食完之後一路等，等左20~25分鐘都未上菜就請店員追吓，佢答：廚師話嚟緊。再等多十分鐘都未到，又再追，之後就嚟到。🙄

菠菜～菜偏老?! 唔係嫩滑
鱈魚～overcooked
薯條～正常
肉眼～叫5X, 嚟左3X❓喺旁邊切左一吓都覺得生，去到中間直頭完全覺得太過份。唔係廚師都睇得出唔係5X熟 ⚠️

我地冇要求換，係因為太了解食肆嘅運作。所以好快食完就走左。真係冇咁過整體差到咁樣，好失望。

#LetsGuide
餐廳有維多利亞港海景及山景，食物質素相對價錢是中上，午餐$138沙律吧任食，如果三文魚主菜加沙律吧都只係二百幾，抵食，傾生意加分，傾心事加親！

A decent and fairly-priced brunch spot. It’s especially good for vegetarians with the choice of Impossible burgers and other non-meat options.

Salad bar/buffet had a solid selection but nothing mindblowing. The seafood wasn’t that tasty and the dessert options definitely need to improve (although you do get to choose a dessert from the brunch menu). Avoid the French Toast here though; it tasted awful compared to everything else we had.

Drinks selection is good but I don’t recall them having a beer. However, the cocktails were tasty, so I didn’t mind so much. 

The view is amazing. Make sure to ask for a window table when booking.
Great views over Hong Kong.  Happy Hour is good value.  Snacks are quite good.
My second time having lunch here, just love the salad bar and the good quality steak with the stunning view, don’t forget to make reservation.

result.name: V-Point

reviews.text: One of the new high rise building consisting of upmarket restaurants.

I had only one drink there, so I can't say much about the food but the view is pretty good and the staff was super friendly. They even made some discount on the occasion of my b-day and offered some shots. I thinks its definitely worth trying, at least, once)
When i asked the concierge where the washroom is , they said there is no washroom in the whole plaza... this is so weird
Great location near Times Square and with a number of eateries, including good Japanese ones like Ootoya.
Is a brand-new landmark in Causeway Bay, surrounded by top restaurants and top fitness centres, highly recommended!!

result.adr_address: 香港銅鑼灣登龍街18號
result.name: V-Point

reviews.text:
豫園 (銅鑼灣)
銅鑼灣登龍街18號 V Point 26樓

招牌松子鮮魚最開胃，可以加碗白飯送汁!

今天本來是去吃火鍋的，不過朋友病了轉了中餐。朋友本來電話去訂位說沒有位不能預訂，但之後我們walk in就有位。這家餐廳是全層分左面廳，右面廳。左面廳全部沒有景，右面廳裝修非常華麗。如果真的要去吃就要訂有景的一邊。

食物方面，我覚得整體ok, 我特別喜歡招牌松子魚，酸酸甜甜一整條，好味。脆皮素鴨也很出色。

如果想食高力豆沙或豆沙鍋餅就要預早叫定好樣廚房準備。那天我們大約10:30pm叫這兩款甜品，全都沒有！
One of the new high rise building consisting of upmarket restaurants.
餐飲為主，但宣傳唔多，下面又冇餐牌可以睇
貴價又難食的高檔菜式

I had only one drink there, so I can't say much about the food but the view is pretty good and the staff was super friendly. They even made some discount on the occasion of my b-day and offered some shots. I thinks its definitely worth trying, at least, once)
